'''Al-Ahli Sports Club''' ({{lang-ar|النادي الأهلي الرياضي}}) is a [[Lebanon|Lebanese]] [[football (soccer)]] club based in [[Sidon]], [[Lebanon]]. Al-Ahli last competed in the [[Lebanese Premier League]] in the [[Lebanese Premier League 2007/08|2007/2008 season]] and was relegated after coming in 12th position. The team currently plays in the [[Lebanese Second Division]].

==Team grounds==
Home matches are normally played in the [[Saida International Stadium]] which can hold up to 22,600 supporters.{{Fact|date=November 2007}}

