'''Chabab Ghazieh Sporting Club''' (in [[Arabic language|Arabic]] نادي الشباب الرياضي الغازيه) is a [[Lebanon|Lebanese]] [[association football|football]] club based in [[Ghazieh]], founded in 1961. The club competes in the [[Lebanese Premier League]] and plays their home matches at the [[Kfarjoz Stadium]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://us.soccerway.com/teams/lebanon/al-shbab-al-qazeia/12551/|title=Lebanon - Chabab Ghazieh Sporting Club - Results, fixtures, squad, statistics, photos, videos and news - Soccerway|website=us.soccerway.com|language=en|access-date=2018-06-23}}</ref>

