{{coord|34|31|27.03|S|56|17|26.55|W|type:landmark_region:UY|display=title}}
'''Estadio Martínez Monegal''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Canelones, Uruguay]].  It is currently used primarily for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Juventud de Las Piedras|Juventud]]. Its capacity is 10,000 spectators.

