{{Infobox football biography | name = Rolston Williams | image = | fullname = | height = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1965|2|3|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Antigua and Barbuda]] | currentclub = | position = [[Midfielder (association football)|Midfielder]] | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = | years1 = | clubs1 = | caps1 = | goals1 = | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = | manageryears1 = 2004 | managerclubs1 = [[Antigua and Barbuda national football team|Antigua and Barbuda]] | manageryears2 = 200?– | managerclubs2 = [[Parham FC]] | manageryears3 = 2010–2011 | managerclubs3 = [[Antigua and Barbuda women's national football team|Antigua and Barbuda women's]] | manageryears4 = 2011 | managerclubs4 = [[Antigua and Barbuda national under-20 football team|Antigua and Barbuda U20]] | manageryears5 = 2012 | managerclubs5 = [[Antigua and Barbuda national under-17 football team|Antigua and Barbuda U17]] | manageryears6 = 2012– | managerclubs6 = [[Antigua and Barbuda national football team|Antigua and Barbuda]] }}
'''Rolston 'Debu' Williams''' (born 3 February 1965) is an [[Antigua and Barbuda|Antiguan and Barbudan]] former professional [[association footballer|football player]] and [[association football manager|manager]].
==Career== In 2004, he coached the [[Antigua and Barbuda national football team]].<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/intldetails/2004nca.html International Matches 2004 - North and Central America and Caribbean - RSSSF]</ref> Later he was a head coach of the [[Parham FC]].<ref>[http://antiguaobserver.com/parhams-poor-scoring-form-makes-williams-uneasy/ Parham’s poor goal-scoring form makes Williams uneasy | Antigua Observer Newspaper]</ref> Also he worked with [[Antigua and Barbuda women's national football team]]<ref>[http://antiguaobserver.com/williams-women%E2%80%99s-team-simply-not-good-enough/ Williams: Women’s team simply not good enough | Antigua Observer Newspaper]</ref> and the U20 and U17 teams.
In November 2012 he again became of the head coach of the Antigua and Barbuda team.<ref>[http://antiguafootball.com/rolston-debu-williams-selected-as-interim-national-team-coach-along-with-the-squad-for-the-upcoming-caribbean-cup/ Rolston Debu Williams selected as Interim National Team Coach along with the squad for the upcoming Caribbean Cup - antiguafootball.com]</ref>
